data.description: Nice 3 bedroom, 2 bath home, all on one level with split bedroom floor plan. All Bedrooms have nice sized walk-in closets. Kitchen has updated appliances, small breakfast bar plus features work island with extra storage in addition to the pantry. Large, privacy fenced back yard, extended concrete patio & in-ground storm shelter. Roof replaced in 2010 and AC & furnace replaced in 2021.  **Legal Description: Lot 51 of Final Plat of River Park Subdivision, Phase I of Lake City, Craighead County, Arkansas as shown by Plat in Deed Record 130 Page 322 at Lake City, Arkansas subject to easements as shown on said plat.
